snippet.title: Lord Of The Mall (Lord Of Them All!) gameplay
snippet.description:
Here's some gameplay of Lord Of The Mall (Lord Of Them All!), a 3D roguelike game that takes place in a shopping mall / dungeon, through the eyes of an old man who walks a fine line between the mists of reality and delusion.

Download on Itch: https://andyman404.itch.io/lord-of-the-mall
